									<p>Three tagin on שעטנזגץ. </p>
									<p>Several majuscular and minuscular letters. </p>
									<p>The names of the sons of Haman arranged in 11 lines, in accordance with the rule. </p>
									<p>Wooden rollers (290mm high). </p>
								</layout>
